pt.ist.fenixframework

Annotation Type NoDomainMetaObjects


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface NoDomainMetaObjects
    THIS ANNOTATION IS FOR INTERNAL USE OF THE FENIX-FRAMEWORK ONLY. Annotates a domain class that is not supposed to have any domain meta data. The framework will not create DomainMetaClasses or DomainMetaObjects for domain classes with this annotation. The class cannot define any consistency predicates.
